content:
Service Intelligence dashboards are data-driven solutions that display key contact center performance metrics.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions

Determine whether you're meeting your customer service goals with easy-to-understand data visualizations in the Service Intelligence dashboards. The combination of customer data, key performance indicators (KPIs), and artificial intelligence (AI) help your service team improve operations and reduce costs.

Service Intelligence Dashboards include:
 
  • Service Intelligence Cases Dashboard: A comprehensive view of your service team’s caseload.
  • Service Intelligence Omni-Channel Dashboard: Quickly identify the routing efficiency and agent performance across Omni-Channel routing and queues.
  • Service Intelligence Einstein Conversation Mining Dashboard: Review key reasons why customers reach out for help with Einstein AI.
  • Service Intelligence Agent Performance Dashboard: See a high-level view of your service team’s performance.
  • Service Intelligence Knowledge Articles Dashboards: Get a comprehensive view of your service team’s knowledge articles.
  • My Performance Dashboard For Agents: As an agent, you can use this dashboard to get a comprehensive view of your caseload.
title: Service Intelligence Dashboards
